<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> cOḻaṉṟalai koṇṭa kOvīrapāṇṭiyaṟku yāṇṭu <hi rend="grantha"><unclear>4</unclear></hi> Itaṉetir 4 Ivvāṇṭu parittikku
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭināṭṭu tēvatāṉan tiruccuḻiyal paḷḷi<unclear>ma</unclear>ṭai cuntarapāṇṭiya Ī<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>rattu tēvarkku veṇpuṉāṭṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kuṭi kiḻavaṉaruḷāḻi taṉ makaṉ kaṇṭaṉ tēvaṉai cārtti vaicca tiruviḷakku Oṉṟu Ivviḷakkukku vaicca Āṭu cāvā mūvāp pē
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rāṭu Irupattaiñcum Aṭai koṇṭa Iṭaiyaṉ paruttikkuṭi nāṭṭup peruñcennilakuṭi kuḻuvāṇai pūti <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Irupattaiñcu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> Ivaiñciṉāl ney cōḻiyanāḻiyāl
<lb n="4"/>ney Āḻākkum Aṭṭuvitāka Iṟaippuṇai paṭṭēṉ tiruccuḻiyal tēvar veṭṭikkuṭi Iṭaiyaṉ Aḻimuṉai caṭai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kuṭi maṇiyaṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
